<P>Geiger
<P>&gt; Being a old man reared on the player kills from the british
<BR>&gt; legends mud on compuserve (yes i am that old), I do not
<BR>&gt; understand the looting of 1 item limit. What is to stop a person
<BR>&gt; that killed another person just to wait untill the other player
<BR>&gt; comes back and gets his/her stuff from his corpse to kill that
<BR>&gt; person again? There are persons out there that will do just
<BR>&gt; that. So if there is a rule against this please educate this old
<BR>&gt; man and if there is not. Why have the 1 item limit? Confucius
<BR>&gt; say PVP is good but would like to know all the rules behind it
<BR>&gt; before playing it.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
